Map Theme: River / Free Style
Maximum Players: 40   (20 CT, 20 T)

Author's Readme/Notes:  A freestyle map where the fun is not when or how fast you get to the end, but how stylish you get there.  With over with over 9 places to go off the main ramp, most of which you must discover, it makes for a GREAT map for testing your skillz, and having fun finding new, and fun routes to take.  This version has a jail, the previous versions are surf_river and surf_river_v2 my other map is confrontal_v3"
